high_descs: Turn to the left and then face the sink on the right.
Pick up the potato from the left side of the sink.
Hold the potato and turn to the left.
Place the potato inside the microwave and shut the door. Open the door and take out the potato. Shut the door.
Hold the potato and turn to the right, to face the sink.
Place the potato inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the stove, then turn right and head to the sink
Pick up the potato on the left
Turn left to face the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave to cook, then take the potato out of the microwave
Turn right to face the sink
Put the potato in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved potato into the sink

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen sink on your left.
Grab the left potato from the counter.
Turn to your left towards the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave, then take it out.
Turn to your right towards the sink.
Put the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Heat a potato and put it in a sink.
